}},"it":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Continua"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Weiter"}},"fr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Continuer"}},"fi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Jatka"}},"nl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Doorgaan"}},"da":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Fortsæt"}},"cs":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Continue"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"继续"}}}},"Currently, you are NOT using a heartbeat mode. A heartbeat is needed to keep %1$@ running in the background. It is recommended to keep enable this feature":{"extractionState":"manual","comment":"Message warning heartbeat disable (1: app name)","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are NOT using a heartbeat mode. A heartbeat is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. It is recommended to keep enable this feature"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"目前，您没有使用心动模式。需要心动才能保持 %%1$@ 在后台运行。 建议保持启用此功能"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"حالياً، أنت لا تستخدم وضع نبض القلب. هناك حاجة إلى نبض القلب لإبقاء %%1$@ قيد التشغيل في الخلفية. من المستحسن الحفاظ على تمكين هذه الميزة"}},"cs":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are NOT using a heartbeat mode. A heartbeat is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. It is recommended to keep enable this feature"}},"da":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"I øjeblikket bruger du IKKE et hjerteslagstilstand. Et hjerteslag er nødvendigt for at holde %%1$@ kørende i baggrunden. Det anbefales at fortsætte med at aktivere denne funktion"}},"nl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Op dit moment gebruikt u GEEN hartslag modus. Een hartenslag is nodig om %%1$@ actief te houden op de achtergrond. Het is aanbevolen om deze functie in te schakelen"}},"fi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Tällä hetkellä et käytä sydämen syke tilaa. Sydämen syke tarvitaan pitämään %%1$@ käynnissä taustalla. On suositeltavaa ottaa tämä ominaisuus käyttöön"}},"fr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Actuellement, vous n'utilisez PAS le mode \"heartbeat\". Un battement de cœur est nécessaire pour que %%1$@ continue à fonctionner en arrière-plan. Il est recommandé de continuer à activer cette fonction"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Momentan verwenden Sie NICHT einen Heartbeat Modus. Ein Heartbeat wird benötigt, um %%1$@ im Hintergrund laufen zu lassen. Es wird empfohlen, diese Funktion weiterhin zu aktivieren"}},"it":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Attualmente, NON stai usando una modalità battito cardiaco. È necessario un battito cardiaco per mantenere %%1$@ in esecuzione sullo sfondo. Si consiglia di mantenere attiva questa funzione"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"現在、あなたはハートビートモードを使用していません。ハートビートは、 %%1$@ をバックグラウンドで実行し続けるために必要です。この機能を有効にしておくことをお勧めします。"}},"nb-NO":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"For øyeblikket bruker du IKKE hjerteslagmodus. Hjerteslag er nødvendig for å holde %%1$@ i gang i bakgrunnen. Det anbefales å fortsette å aktivere denne funksjonen"}},"pl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Obecnie NIE używasz trybu bicia serca. Potrzebne jest bicie serca, aby %%1$@ działał w tle. Zalecane jest utrzymanie tej funkcji"}},"pt-BR":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Atualmente, você NÃO está usando um modo pulso. Uma batida cardíaca é necessária para manter %%1$@ a rodar em segundo plano. Recomenda-se manter ativado esse recurso"}},"ro":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"În prezent, NU folosiți un mod de bătăi ale inimii. O bătăi ale inimii este necesară pentru a menține %%1$@ în fundal. Este recomandat să continuați activarea acestei funcții"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"В данный момент вы НЕ используете режим heartbeat. Для продолжения работы %%1$@ в фоновом режиме, необходимо использовать heartbeat. Рекомендуется включить эту функцию"}},"sk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"V súčasnosti NEPOUŽÍVATE režim heartbeat. Heartbeat je potrebný na to, aby %%1$@ bežal na pozadí. Odporúča sa ponechať túto funkciu zapnutú"}},"sl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Trenutno NE uporabljate načina srčnega utripa. Srčni utrip je potreben, da %%1$@ deluje v ozadju. Priporočljivo je, da še naprej omogočate to funkcijo"}},"es":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Actualmente, NO estás usando un modo latido del corazón. Se necesita un latido del corazón para mantener %%1$@ funcionando en segundo plano. Se recomienda mantener activa esta función"}},"sv":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"För närvarande använder du INTE ett hjärtslagsläge. Ett hjärtslag behövs för att hålla %%1$@ igång i bakgrunden. Det rekommenderas att behålla den här funktionen"}},"tr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Şu anda bir kalp atışı modu KULLANMIYORSUNUZ. %%1$@ 'un arka planda çalışmaya devam etmesi için bir kalp atışı gereklidir. Bu özelliği etkinleştirmeye devam etmeniz önerilir"}},"uk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Наразі ви НЕ використовуєте режим серцебиття. Серцебиття потрібне для того, щоб %%1$@ працював у фоновому режимі. Рекомендується залишити цю функцію увімкненою"}},"vi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are NOT using a heartbeat mode. A heartbeat is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. It is recommended to keep enable this feature"}},"nb":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"For tiden bruker du IKKE hjerteslag. Et hjerterytme er nødvendig for å holde %%1$@ kjører i bakgrunnen. Det er anbefalt å holde aktivere denne funksjonen"}}}},"Currently, you are using a heartbeat mode. This is needed to keep %1$@ running in the background. This might be interesting if your CGM already provides a heartbeat. It is recommended to keep this feature enabled":{"extractionState":"manual","comment":"Message warning heartbeat disable (1: app name)","localizations":{"nb-NO":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"For øyeblikket bruker du en heartbeat-modus. Dette er nødvendig for å holde %%1$@ i gang i bakgrunnen. Dette kan være interessant hvis CGM-en din allerede gir hjerteslag. Det anbefales å beholde denne funksjonen aktivert"}},"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are using a heartbeat mode. This is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. This might be interesting if your CGM already provides a heartbeat. It is recommended to keep this feature enabled"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"目前，您正在使用心跳模式。这需要保持 %%1$@ 在后台运行。 如果您的 CGM 已经提供了一个心声，这可能是有趣的。建议保持启用此功能"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"حاليا، أنت تستخدم وضع نبض القلب. هذا مطلوب لإبقاء %%1$@ قيد التشغيل في الخلفية. قد يكون هذا مثيراً للاهتمام إذا كان CGM الخاص بك يوفر مسبقاً نبض القلب. من المستحسن إبقاء هذه الميزة ممكنة"}},"cs":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are using a heartbeat mode. This is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. This might be interesting if your CGM already provides a heartbeat. It is recommended to keep this feature enabled"}},"da":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"I øjeblikket bruger du et hjerteslagstilstand. Dette er nødvendigt for at holde %%1$@ kørende i baggrunden. Dette kan være interessant, hvis din CGM allerede giver et hjerteslag. Det anbefales at holde denne funktion aktiveret"}},"nl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Op dit moment gebruikt u een hartbeet modus. Dit is nodig om %%1$@ actief te houden op de achtergrond. Dit kan interessant zijn als uw CGM al een hartenslag biedt. Het wordt aangeraden om deze functie ingeschakeld te houden"}},"fi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Tällä hetkellä käytät syke tilaa. Tämä on tarpeen pitää %%1$@ käynnissä taustalla. Tämä saattaa olla mielenkiintoista, jos CGM jo tarjoaa sykkeen. On suositeltavaa pitää tämä ominaisuus käytössä"}},"fr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Actuellement, vous utilisez un mode de pulsation cardiaque. Ceci est nécessaire pour garder %%1$@ en cours d'exécution en arrière-plan. Cela pourrait être intéressant si votre MGC fournit déjà un coup de cœur. Il est recommandé de garder cette fonctionnalité activée"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Zurzeit verwenden Sie einen Heartbeat-Modus. Dieser wird benötigt, um %%1$@ im Hintergrund laufen zu lassen. Dies könnte interessant sein, wenn Ihr CGM bereits einen Herzschlag liefert. Es wird empfohlen, diese Funktion aktiviert zu lassen"}},"it":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Attualmente, stai usando una modalità battito cardiaco. Questo è necessario per mantenere %%1$@ in esecuzione in background. Questo potrebbe essere interessante se il vostro CGM fornisce già un battito cardiaco. Si consiglia di mantenere questa funzione abilitata"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"現在、あなたはハートビートモードを使用しています。これは、 %%1$@ をバックグラウンドで実行し続けるために必要です。お使いの CGM がすでにハートビートを提供している場合、これは興味深いかもしれません。この機能は有効にしておくことをお勧めします。"}},"pl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Obecnie używasz trybu bicia serca. Jest to konieczne, aby %%1$@ działał w tle. To może być interesujące, jeśli Twój CGM już zapewnia bicie serca. Zaleca się, aby ta funkcja była włączona"}},"pt-BR":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Atualmente, você está usando um modo de pulso. Isto é necessário para manter %%1$@ em execução em segundo plano. Isso pode ser interessante se seu CGM já fornecer um batimento cardíaco. É recomendado manter este recurso ativado"}},"nb":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"For tiden bruker du en hjertefrekvensmodus. Dette er nødvendig for at %%1$@ skal kunne kjøre i bakgrunnen. Dette kan være interessant hvis CGM allerede tilbyr en hjerterytme. Det anbefales å holde denne funksjonen aktivert"}},"ro":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"În prezent, folosiți un mod de bătăi ale inimii. Acest lucru este necesar pentru a menține %%1$@ să ruleze în fundal. Acest lucru poate fi interesant dacă CGM vă oferă deja o bătăi de inimă. Este recomandat să păstrați această caracteristică activată"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"В данный момент вы используете режим heartbeat. Необходимо держать %%1$@ в фоновом режиме. Это может быть интересно если ваш CGM уже предоставляет сердечный процесс. Рекомендуется сохранить эту функцию"}},"sk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"V súčasnosti používate režim heartbeat. Je to potrebné na to, aby %%1$@ bežal na pozadí. To môže byť zaujímavé, ak Váš CGM už poskytuje heartbeat. Odporúča sa nechať túto funkciu zapnutú"}},"sl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Trenutno uporabljate način srčnega utripa. Ta način je potreben, da %%1$@ deluje v ozadju. To je lahko zanimivo, če vaš CGM že zagotavlja srčni utrip. Priporočljivo je, da ta funkcija ostane omogočena"}},"es":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Actualmente estás usando un modo latido del corazón. Esto es necesario para mantener %%1$@ funcionando en segundo plano. Esto podría ser interesante si su CGM ya proporciona un latido de corazón. Se recomienda mantener esta función habilitada"}},"sv":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"För närvarande använder du ett hjärtslagsläge. Detta behövs för att hålla %%1$@ igång i bakgrunden. Detta kan vara intressant om din CGM redan ger ett hjärtslag. Det rekommenderas att hålla denna funktion aktiverad"}},"tr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Şu anda bir kalp atışı modu kullanıyorsunuz. Bu, %%1$@ adresini arka planda çalışır durumda tutmak için gereklidir. CGM'niz zaten bir kalp atışı sağlıyorsa bu ilginç olabilir. Bu özelliğin etkin tutulması tavsiye edilir"}},"uk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Наразі ви використовуєте режим серцебиття. Це потрібно для того, щоб %%1$@ працював у фоновому режимі. Це може бути корисно, якщо ваш CGM вже надає сигнал серцебиття. Рекомендується залишити цю функцію увімкненою"}},"vi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Currently, you are using a heartbeat mode. This is needed to keep %%1$@ running in the background. This might be interesting if your CGM already provides a heartbeat. It is recommended to keep this feature enabled"}}}},"Deactivate Patch":{"extractionState":"manual","comment":"deactivate patch","localizations":{"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"停用补丁"}},"nb":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiver programfiks"}},"vi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate Patch"}},"uk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Деактивувати патч"}},"tr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Yamayı Devre Dışı Bırak"}},"sv":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Inaktivera Patch"}},"es":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Desactivar parche"}},"sl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiviranje obliža"}},"sk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktivovať náplasť"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Отключить патч"}},"ro":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Dezactivați patch-ul"}},"pt-BR":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Desativar Correção"}},"pl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Dezaktywuj Patch"}},"nb-NO":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiver lapp"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"パッチの無効化"}},"it":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Disattiva Patch"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Patch deaktivieren"}},"fr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Désactiver le correctif"}},"fi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Poista Paikkaus Käytöstä"}},"nl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Patch deactiveren"}},"da":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiver Patch"}},"cs":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate Patch"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"إلغاء تنشيط التصحيح"}},"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate Patch"}}}},"Deactivate patch":{"extractionState":"manual","comment":"Header deactivate patch","localizations":{"en":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate patch"}},"nb":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktivere patch"}},"vi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate patch"}},"uk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Деактивувати патч"}},"tr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Yamayı devre dışı bırak"}},"sv":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Inaktivera patch"}},"es":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Desactivar parche"}},"sl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiviranje obliža"}},"sk":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktivovať náplasť"}},"ru":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Деактивировать патч"}},"ro":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Dezactivați patch-ul"}},"pt-BR":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Desativar o patch"}},"pl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Dezaktywuj łatkę"}},"nb-NO":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiver plaster"}},"ja":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"パッチの無効化"}},"it":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Disattiva patch"}},"de":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Patch deaktivieren"}},"fr":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Désactiver le patch"}},"fi":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Poista paikannus käytöstä"}},"nl":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Patch deactiveren"}},"da":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deaktiver patch"}},"cs":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"Deactivate patch"}},"ar":{"stringUnit":{"state":"translated","value":"إلغاء تنشيط التصحيح"}},"zh-Hans":{"stringUnit":{"sta